author: Lateisha Snell
title: Lateisha Snell
text: Great employees make a business great. Nick, hopefully i didn't get the name wrong, was extremely helpful, nothing was difficult. He helped me understand what i needed to know.Nick walked me threw it all, I didn't get a chance to work with the others but the were professional, and friendly also. Its not my first time or last time using ur company. That day was difficult for me, I'm glad to say I felt my belongings will be secure at ur facility. So I'm resting easy.Thanks. (salute to Nick)
